  "texts": [
    "In a retrospective study of 435 women, Kawakami et al. (2019) confirmed the power of popular ML classifiers in epithelial ovarian cancer diagnosis using 32 preoperative blood biomarkers before any initial intervention.",
    "Song et al. (2018) explored 16 serum biomarker profiles in search of alternative marker pairings to lessen misdiagnosis.",
    "In another study, Aljakouch et al. (2019) revealed the potential of all Raman spectra, CARS, SHG, and TPF imaging as fast non-invasive CxCa diagnosis tools.",
    "Elias et al. (2017) suggested circulating miRNAs to establish a non-invasive OC diagnostic test, if it is validated, it could also screen women at high risk.",
    "Other research for precise diagnoses through non-or minimally invasive modalities has been undertaken, e.g."
  ]
